{"tid":1973484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發！］中聯辦副主任楊健被國務院免職","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:59:19.000Z","uid":191474,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a3237dc8af8b0bea3b53e087939a2d473ac78aeb","tid":1973484,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"國務院今日（１５日）下午宣佈免去中聯辦副主任楊健的職務。<br />\n<br />\n楊健於1958年出生江西安福。1975年11月參加工作，中央黨校研究生學歷，曾任新華社江西分社及廣東分社社長，自2013年出任中聯辦副主任一職，已在該位近7年時間。<br />\n<br />\n楊健被免去職務後，中聯辦還包括陳冬、楊健平、仇鴻、盧新寧、譚鐵牛及何靖六名副主任。"},{"pid":"4a787de8d2d7ded687c15fc514c35c9a064485db","tid":1973484,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"只會換個更硬嘅上嚟"},{"pid":"6b129299eb4a8d7fa119844c9d90c3cc997c77ac","tid":1973484,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"成7個副主任？"},{"pid":"d25eba92404c81780f7d775e068cb714bd13f753","tid":1973484,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"東網都有報<br />\n我唔放link上來了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/15/162756_4abc35cf851146d3248969c8420a0be5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2F162756_4abc35cf851146d3248969c8420a0be5.png&h=884f6150&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"062e6a77979fa4409458ddb4f363a32b9ecb22ec","tid":1973484,"uid":21398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6b129299eb4a8d7fa119844c9d90c3cc997c77ac","tid":1973484,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"成7個副主任？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係袋錢位<br />\n打打嘴炮，有撚野做咩"},{"pid":"bc7e04377f8a2d5bd6b6acf4d0b59faedb10e3ec","tid":1973484,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"中聯辦前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c